description:
Squid Squad OG is a play-to-earn game where players fight each other in a Battle royale tournament based on Rock, Paper, Scissor. This batch has been created for the second game. 

The NFTs have been created by our graphic designers and handpicked to create the best collection on the “Squids vacation on the human world” theme.

Utility:
These NFTs are required  to play the  Squid Squad OG season 2.  These NFTs are not eligible for the game 3 or further game if they haven’t participated in the game 2 first. 

All NFT owners will need to register their Squid for the game. By doing so, the game smart contract will take the authority on the NFT. He will give you back the NFT, with added traits if it survives the game. 

Failure to register your NFT for the next game will result in your Squid losing his value and his metadata. So make sure to register for the game before the 26th of June. 

How do I play the game?
Visit app.squidsquadog.com and follow the guide.
name: Squid Squad OG 2
